{"tid":1487072,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［公投］下一步係set deadline ，入嚟投票揀邊日","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T06:47:29.000Z","uid":135306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c27ad7bc8f1112b039da19f3b8973ecaa5da145e","tid":1487072,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:07:50.000Z","msg":"次次都話和理非 &mdash;&gt; Deadline &mdash;&gt; 勇武<br />\n點解熱門一個關於deadline 嘅post都冇！？<br />\n<br />\n琴日逾170萬人和理非遊行嘅作用係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對前線行動升級嘅民意授權</span></span></strong><br />\n大家要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">好好運用set deadline，令行動升級變得更加出師有名，名正言順</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我建議應該係820/ 821/ 822 揀一日做deadline， 而我個人提議揀822，因為：<br />\n1. 宜家已經19號 畀返兩三日政府會更合理 （820不合適，太急）<br />\n2. 823 開始先有重大行動 （823 後不合適）<br />\n<br />\n大家唔同意呢三日嘅都請你留個言解釋下，覺得set deadline係重要嘅麻煩幫手推上熱門。<br />\n<br />\n另外，我覺得set deadline 外可以加埋<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出聲明/ 民間記者會，講到明係因為政府多次唔回應200萬人嘅訴求，勇武先逼於無奈升級！<br />\n</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></strong>"},{"pid":"1a86aac67b05996be178c3e30df07064de748b7c","tid":1487072,"uid":135306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"Deadline: 820"},{"pid":"981b4808b9a1e15a29532b3815f4bebdf333b556","tid":1487072,"uid":135306,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"Deadline: 821"},{"pid":"d621ea5997b6eec0bd0b0328f5de3f4270d3ed56","tid":1487072,"uid":135306,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:09:10.000Z","msg":"Deadline: 822"},{"pid":"b86740ff1cba58b63389603c3347e58fc052d711","tid":1487072,"uid":135306,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"reply